channel.title: SerpentScape - 317 - Need Staff
channel.description:
Hey! Serpentscape opened a day ago. It currently has no known bugs and contains a lot of awesome features like pvp ranks inside the game, boss logs for PVM'ers, Slayer points and Boss Slayer points, loyalty points system and overall a server for anyone - Skillers, PvP'ers and PVM'ers.
Promo video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jP7jlPUTZxA
Homepage: Serpentscape.com
Forums: SerpentScape.com/forums/
The forums also include a wide variety of sections for you every need. Come and check it out!
